Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:45.77,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}The blue moon illuminated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:49.73,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}your wandering shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:54.24,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}I could never tell you all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:59.16,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,250)}It was so very frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.04,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}I think about your faked smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:07.67,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}and forget all the hot tears we shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.34,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}What do these empty husks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:16.18,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}those empty eyes of yours, reflect, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:21.39,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}The transient quarter moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.56,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,100)}hides in a rift in the clouds,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.94,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(100,300)}as darkness seeps up from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:30.40,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}Tell me the truth, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:32.57,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}Are you so despondent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:37.03,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,0)}that you still sit alone, sighing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:19.25,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}Without you, I just can’t smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:30.31,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I walk this banal town,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:36.39,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}feeling such intense emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:42.78,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I know that if I could treasure them and live on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:52.08,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I would need nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:22:00.25,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}The summer flowers that bloomed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:06.55,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}Come falling down, dancing in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:09.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I can barely recall the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:13.18,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}where they all came tumbling down,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:24.03,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}so what I can still recall is all the more precious.
